{"tid":692271,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一人n個幫陌生人/比陌生人幫嘅經歷 (2)","createTime":"2018-06-06T13:10:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-01T06:14:09.000Z","uid":28366,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"63f9d2e73c879c2819ec91f26a7974c63ecd6f44","tid":692271,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T13:10:57.000Z","msg":"上個post:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/76780/14?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/76780/14?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\n有次落大雨唔知點解冇帶遮但係得件雨褸，之後行到落樓下見到個女仔冇帶遮好慘咁企左係到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之後俾左件野佢就走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"687ed562e81424328af73196e1c18f0c42535cb7","tid":692271,"uid":51981,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T13:21:20.000Z","msg":"第一次去英國旅行on99咁帶左個喼去<br />\n一見到天壇大佛咁長既樓梯就知道gg<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好彩有個大叔幫我拎上地面 <br />\n見佢拎到面紅曬咁勁唔好意思<br />\n多謝你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5ace5dba26a94f1de796d07c6e2031b96bee984","tid":692271,"uid":170229,"like":9,"dislike":4,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T14:51:40.000Z","msg":"用垃圾國語幫班唔識英文嘅台灣遊客係外國帶路，順面一齊屌中共老母"},{"pid":"16b5195360cdd5a807103fb9411547e666950151","tid":692271,"uid":134484,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T14:57:23.000Z","msg":"喺街落大雨無遮有人遮我去地鐵站"},{"pid":"960f476701158286139a55d6fb6ae346a5165414","tid":692271,"uid":28366,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T06:57:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d95653dfef12c075c7fb1cce950b6b64f5af2114","tid":692271,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T00:45:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab5e4174fe717287d698b022f7cbd9f4e72de95e","tid":692271,"uid":84189,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T00:49:51.000Z","msg":"有時行街見到人地一家人影相少緊個人，可能係爸爸揸相機影老婆仔女呢啲，我都會主動行過去話可以幫佢地影張全家福"},{"pid":"6cbee767038c2769a78f7222ff9b199b7a804150","tid":692271,"uid":131955,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T00:58:40.000Z","msg":"個日飲完茶同屋企人分開等緊朋友無啦啦想嘔<br />\n又用曬紙巾<br />\n問左個陌生男人令紙巾 之後佢仲買左枝水比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好人有好報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3e62769ccf1579f0c9415c118e770dcce89bde9","tid":692271,"uid":171838,"like":23,"dislike":14,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T04:33:00.000Z","msg":"呢個好深刻，令我對大陸人改觀既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當時自己一個第一次去Seoul旅行，去到真係大陸咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n落機搭地鐵去民宿，點知過左夜晚11點，<br />\n未到終點站就要即刻落車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當時條街又黑又靜，又唔知去左邊，一個人拖住大大個gip，截黎截去都截唔到Taxi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(韓國的士仲衰過香港的士，揀客戴，而且好多唔識英文，覺得載遊客好麻煩，會揀返戴本地人)<br />\n<br />\n馬路身後面有間餐廳，兩個韓國男人坐係度食煙收拾緊，我已經好驚，咁岩有兩個韓妹行過黎望住我，我以為想幫我啦，點知原來同我搶Taxi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢個時候後面個男人走上前用韓文同我講野<br />\n我聽唔明，又用返英文同佢講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢又唔明<br />\n雞同鴨講左一輪之後，我拎電話google translate <br />\n佢見到我打中文即刻用普通話講 : 妳懂中文？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n原來佢係大陸人黎韓國好多年，跟住佢個fd又出埋黎<br />\n兩個幫我拎埋個gip，一抽二袋過對面多條街截的士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實當時都仲好驚會唔會俾人賣豬仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但最後佢好好咁幫我同的士司機溝通<br />\n<br />\n到左民宿我入左房，<br />\n個host仲話有個人打左好多次比佢問我到左未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我好感動，原來大陸人都有好好既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過佢係民宿電話問我安全未，同可以帶我出去玩<br />\n又留左wechat比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我最後都冇加到佢"},{"pid":"aa098b59b0dd989d5c0e9a17e58952857ff8f6af","tid":692271,"uid":171838,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T04:46:54.000Z","msg":"點解負皮既，因為大陸人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c99075dadc453fb35633823297cb21d7f41ce7f","tid":692271,"uid":50376,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T08:17:26.000Z","msg":"搭搭下巴士<br />\n前面有個坐四個位面對面既妹妹突然間嘔<br />\n嘔中左坐佢對面兩公婆個老婆對鞋<br />\n個呀媽係咁道歉係咁清理<br />\n個老婆就無嬲既，只係急於清理自己對鞋<br />\n咁岩我係12蚊店買完野，有成大包濕紙巾<br />\n就比左個兩公婆同個媽媽清理現場<br />\n其實個下都覺得香港人雖然係冷漠<br />\n但至少架車到無人會出聲怪個妹妹呀、埋怨好臭呀咁<br />\n都算係咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2396250031581254359d293efcea1cf439b19556","tid":692271,"uid":136933,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T08:23:26.000Z","msg":"中學返學落大雨 見到有個同學冇遮 遮埋佢<br />\n行緊既時候都有傾幾句<br />\n點知佢一返到學校 唔該拜拜都冇句就影都冇埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"088a05e087c98903798f37bd387f7e223ea7cb40","tid":692271,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2396250031581254359d293efcea1cf439b19556","tid":692271,"uid":136933,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T08:23:26.000Z","msg":"中學返學落大雨 見到有個同學冇遮 遮埋佢<br />\n行緊既時候都有傾幾句<br />\n點知佢一返到學校 唔該拜拜都冇句就影都冇埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T08:45:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4242783c4c5a2527f24e5189ebab4933a1622774","tid":692271,"uid":189794,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy"